                            <comment id="14071963" author="tripod" created="Wed, 23 Jul 2014 17:01:17 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;added test case in r1612873&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14072898" author="anchela" created="Thu, 24 Jul 2014 06:52:56 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;i will take a look during the oakathon next week.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14076235" author="anchela" created="Mon, 28 Jul 2014 13:57:19 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;rev. 1614032&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14076545" author="tripod" created="Mon, 28 Jul 2014 18:29:05 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;thanks, but why did you remove the &lt;tt&gt;TokenLoginModuleTest#testValidTokenCredentialsCaseInsensitive()&lt;/tt&gt; test ?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14076821" author="anchela" created="Mon, 28 Jul 2014 20:52:12 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;because the bug was in tokenprovider and i prefer to have tests where they actually belong.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14077058" author="tripod" created="Mon, 28 Jul 2014 22:44:10 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;...but we should test the entire login-chain, not only the underlying bits.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14077438" author="anchela" created="Tue, 29 Jul 2014 06:39:45 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;sure... but your test didn&apos;t do that. it tested TokenProvider#createToken. feel free to add another test which does:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;login(cred-with-upper-case-uid-and-request-for-token-generation)&lt;br/&gt;
extract-login-token&lt;br/&gt;
logout&lt;br/&gt;
login(with-tokencredentials)&lt;br/&gt;
logout&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14159960" author="amitjain" created="Mon, 6 Oct 2014 04:09:29 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Bulk close for 1.1.0&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14496242" author="anchela" created="Wed, 15 Apr 2015 14:30:24 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;merged changes (plus additionally 1599160 which was required by the test-cases) into 1.0 branch at rev. 1673782&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
